msgstr "订阅设置"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:281
msgid "Subscription & Recurring Payment"
msgstr "订阅和定期付款"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:285
msgid ""
"Enable automatic recurring payment (⚠️ Requires Alipay Recurring Payment "
"service)"
msgstr "启用自动定期付款（⚠️需要支付宝定期付款服务）"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:289
msgid "Personal Product Code"
msgstr "个人产品代码"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:291
msgid ""
"Product code provided by Alipay after signing recurring payment contract. "
"Common values: GENERAL_WITHHOLDING_P (general withholding). Leave empty if "
"not using recurring agreement."
msgstr ""
"支付宝签订循环付款合同后提供的产品代码。常用值：GENERAL_WITHHOLDING_P（一般预"
"扣）。如不使用循环协议，请留空。"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:299
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "它是如何工作的"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:311
msgid "Alipay Recurring Agreement Process:"
msgstr "支付宝定期协议流程："

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:312
msgid "Initial purchase: Customer signs recurring agreement + first payment"
msgstr "首次购买：客户签署定期协议+首付款"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:313
msgid "Auto renewal: System automatically deducts payment on billing date"
msgstr "自动续订：系统在账单日自动扣款"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:314
msgid ""
"Cancellation: Customer can cancel agreement anytime from their Alipay app"
msgstr "取消：客户可以随时通过支付宝应用程序取消协议"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:315
msgid ""
"Fallback: If agreement deduction fails, customer receives manual payment "
"notification"
msgstr "后备方案：如果协议扣款失败，客户将收到手动付款通知"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:316
msgid ""
"Note: Without this feature, all renewals require manual payment by customer."
msgstr "注意：如果没有此功能，所有续订都需要客户手动付款。"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:325
msgid ""
"Automatically cancel subscription when parent order is canceled (Initial "
"order only)"
msgstr "当父订单取消时自动取消订阅（仅限初始订单）"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:326
msgid ""
"When enabled, canceling the initial subscription order will automatically "
"cancel the associated subscription. This does NOT affect renewal orders - "
"canceling a renewal order will never cancel the subscription."
msgstr ""
"启用后，取消初始订阅订单将自动取消相关订阅。这不会影响续订订单——取消续订订单"
"永远不会取消订阅。"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:330
msgid "Order Cancellation Rules"
msgstr "订单取消规则"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:343
msgid "Automatic Subscription Cancellation Rules:"
msgstr "自动取消订阅规则："

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:344
msgid ""
"✅ WILL cancel: Initial subscription order (type=subscription) is canceled"
msgstr "✅ 将取消：初始订阅订单（type=subscription）被取消"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:345
msgid "❌ Will NOT cancel: Renewal order (type=renewal) is canceled"
msgstr "❌ 不会取消：续订订单（type=renewal）被取消"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:346
msgid "❌ Will NOT cancel: Subscription already in canceled status"
msgstr "❌ 不会取消：订阅已处于取消状态"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:347
msgid "❌ Will NOT cancel: Orders from other payment methods"
msgstr "❌ 不会取消：其他付款方式的订单"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:348
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "注意："

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:349
msgid ""
"This feature helps maintain data consistency between orders and "
"subscriptions. All operations are logged in the order activity log."
msgstr ""
"此功能有助于维护订单和订阅之间的数据一致性。所有操作都记录在订单活动日志中。"

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:350
msgid "Default:"
msgstr "默认："

#: src/Gateway/AlipayGateway.php:351
msgid ""
"This feature is DISABLED by default. Enable it only if you need automatic "
"synchronization between order and subscription status."
msgstr "此功能默认禁用。仅当您需要订单和订阅状态自动同步时才启用。"

